| 37. Find the product of digits using recursion   | Find the product of the digits of a number using recursion.                                                                                                  | Input: 123, Output: 6 (1 * 2 * 3)                                                                                                                                                                                            |
| 38. Check if a number is palindrome using recursion | Check if a number is palindrome using recursion.                                                                                                            | Input: 121, Output: Palindrome                                                                                                                                                                                               |
| 39. Sum of squares of N numbers using recursion  | Sum the squares of the first N numbers using recursion.                                                                                                      | Input: N = 3, Output: 14                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
