| 41. Find LCM using recursion                     | Find the least common multiple of two numbers using recursion.                                                                                               | Input: 4, 6; Output: 12                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
| 42. Find the sum of the first N odd numbers using recursion | Sum the first N odd numbers using recursion.                                                                                                                | Input: N

